  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged : 50 to 74 years.

          -  Not having ever been invited to participate in colorectal screening.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who have a Fecal Occult Blood Test for less than 2 years or a colonoscopy
             within the past 5 years or excluded for medical reasons (according to information
             known from ADECA).
      </textblock>
